snippet.title: Best VGM 266 - Maniac Mansion - Dave's Theme
snippet.description:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iN3Jp55Db_A&fmt=18 for the HQ version!

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES
Maniac Mansion
Dave's Theme (Fat Patty - The Boys are Still Back)
